{
  "texts": [
    "As the performance of GPT-4 varies over time, this could reduce generalizability [36].",
    "Finally, in this study, we compared GPT-4's performance with that of medical students by using the difficulty index of each exam question.",
    "It is important to note that this difficulty index is specific to the particular cohort of medical students who participated in the representative exam.",
    "ConclusionIn summary, we found that GPT-4 performs extremely well on psychosomatic medicine questions.",
    "Questions answered correctly by GPT-4 were also easier for human students than questions answered incorrectly, as shown by the level of question difficulty."
  ]
}